/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/105903_facfa67f594f2f99b4884919ae768b73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F105903_facfa67f594f2f99b4884919ae768b73.png&h=f30e9e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杯花生醬終於正常返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/110033_a8343a06c92634e8a204a48df3a66c14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F110033_a8343a06c92634e8a204a48df3a66c14.png&h=cf1e2b22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n奶茶唔洗講啦⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">迎接一個好周末</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a631baf7cc9d04dcd7fb2f151280ccd4855e2c","tid":648704,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"老人家上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21bfa7f19e5d684c056d58087ea9bea253294b0","tid":648704,"uid":133522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61a631baf7cc9d04dcd7fb2f151280ccd4855e2c","tid":648704,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"老人家上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"唔得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（拎屋企人張卡去用咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"}]}